                                        <span aria-hidden="true" class='stats-item-numbers-stat numscroller' data-min='1' data-max='46' data-delay='5' data-increment='5'>46</span>
                                        <span aria-hidden="true" class="stats-item-numbers-unit">%</span>
                                        <span class='stats-item-numbers-stat sronly'>46%</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="stats-item-description">of Welsh-speaking pupils enjoy sports outside the curriculum three times a week</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="stats-item">
                                    <div class="stats-item-numbers">
                                        <span aria-hidden="true" class='stats-item-numbers-stat numscroller' data-min='1' data-max='53' data-delay='5' data-increment='5'>53</span>
