    <div class="flexibleblocks-block __accordions ">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row __center">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6">
                    <h2 class="h4 accordions-heading __animatefade __stagger1 __animatein">How to increase the use of Welsh in sports club?</h2>
                            <div class="accordion Accordion __animatefade __stagger1 __animatein">
                                <button class="accordion-head AccordionTrigger" id="accordion-button-1" aria-controls="accordion-panel-1" aria-expanded="false">
                                    <span>Our online tool</span>
                                </button>
                                <div class="accordion-content AccordionContent" id="accordion-panel-1" aria-labelledby="accordion-button-1" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
                                    <div class="usercontent">
                                        <p>Do you need a bit more help?  Use our <a href="/media/vkse5bb3/amdani.pdf" title="Amdani!">practical pack</a> for sports clubs and associations. </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion Accordion __animatefade __stagger1 __animatein">
                                <button class="accordion-head AccordionTrigger" id="accordion-button-2" aria-controls="accordion-panel-2" aria-expanded="false">
                                    <span>Our helpsheet</span>
                                </button>
                                <div class="accordion-content AccordionContent" id="accordion-panel-2" aria-labelledby="accordion-button-2" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
                                    <div class="usercontent">
                                        <p><a href="/media/gpblvsgl/pwyntiau-gweithredu-chwaraeon-sports-action-points-1.pdf?id=%2Fsites%2FTimHybu%2FShared%20Documents%2FGeneral%2FCanllawiau%20ac%20ymchwil%2FCanllawiau%2FPwyntiau%20gweithredu%20Chwaraeon%20%2D%20Sports%20Action%20Points%2Epdf&amp;parent=%2Fsites%2FTimHybu%2FShared%20Documents%2FGeneral%2FCanllawiau%20ac%20ymchwil%2FCanllawiau&amp;p=true&amp;ga=1" title="Pwyntiau Gweithredu Chwaraeon Sports Action Points (1)" data-anchor="?id=%2Fsites%2FTimHybu%2FShared%20Documents%2FGeneral%2FCanllawiau%20ac%20ymchwil%2FCanllawiau%2FPwyntiau%20gweithredu%20Chwaraeon%20%2D%20Sports%20Action%20Points%2Epdf&amp;parent=%2Fsites%2FTimHybu%2FShared%20Documents%2FGeneral%2FCanllawiau%20ac%20ymchwil%2FCanllawiau&amp;p=true&amp;ga=1">Our helpsheet</a> which will give you a few quick and easy ideas on where to start.  Ideas include, find out who speaks Welsh at your club, using some simple Welsh phrases in your social media messages, and much more.</p>
<p> </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="accordion Accordion __animatefade __stagger1 __animatein">
                                <button class="accordion-head AccordionTrigger" id="accordion-button-3" aria-controls="accordion-panel-3" aria-expanded="false">
                                    <span>Additional support</span>
                                </button>
                                <div class="accordion-content AccordionContent" id="accordion-panel-3" aria-labelledby="accordion-button-3" aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
                                    <div class="usercontent">
                                        <p>Get in touch with the Hybu team for further support to develop your Welsh Language services. We can arrange a meeting to discuss your next steps: <strong><a href="mailto:hybu@cyg-wlc.cymru">hybu@cyg-wlc.cymru</a></strong></p>
<p><span> </span></p>
<p><span>There are also </span><strong><a href="https://www.sport.wales/grants-and-funding/club-support/club-solutions-templates/">other useful documents</a></strong><span> available on the Sport Wales website</span></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

